57#if defined(_KERNEL) || defined(_STANDALONE)
58#include <sys/param.h>
59#include <sys/types.h>
60#include <lib/libkern/libkern.h>
61#else
62#include <stddef.h>
63#include <stdint.h>
64#include <stdlib.h>
65#include <string.h>
66#endif
67
68#ifdef __CHECKER__
69#define FDT_FORCE __attribute__((force))
70#define FDT_BITWISE __attribute__((bitwise))
71#else
72#define FDT_FORCE
73#define FDT_BITWISE
74#endif
75
76typedef uint16_t FDT_BITWISE fdt16_t;
77typedef uint32_t FDT_BITWISE fdt32_t;
78typedef uint64_t FDT_BITWISE fdt64_t;
79
80#define EXTRACT_BYTE(x, n) ((unsigned long long)((uint8_t *)&x)[n])
81#define CPU_TO_FDT16(x) ((EXTRACT_BYTE(x, 0) << 8) | EXTRACT_BYTE(x, 1))
82#define CPU_TO_FDT32(x) ((EXTRACT_BYTE(x, 0) << 24) | (EXTRACT_BYTE(x, 1) << 16) | \
83 (EXTRACT_BYTE(x, 2) << 8) | EXTRACT_BYTE(x, 3))
84#define CPU_TO_FDT64(x) ((EXTRACT_BYTE(x, 0) << 56) | (EXTRACT_BYTE(x, 1) << 48) | \
85 (EXTRACT_BYTE(x, 2) << 40) | (EXTRACT_BYTE(x, 3) << 32) | \
86 (EXTRACT_BYTE(x, 4) << 24) | (EXTRACT_BYTE(x, 5) << 16) | \
87 (EXTRACT_BYTE(x, 6) << 8) | EXTRACT_BYTE(x, 7))
88
89static inline uint16_t fdt16_to_cpu(fdt16_t x)
90{
91 return (FDT_FORCE uint16_t)CPU_TO_FDT16(x);
92}
93static inline fdt16_t cpu_to_fdt16(uint16_t x)
94{
95 return (FDT_FORCE fdt16_t)CPU_TO_FDT16(x);
96}
97
98static inline uint32_t fdt32_to_cpu(fdt32_t x)
99{
100 return (FDT_FORCE uint32_t)CPU_TO_FDT32(x);
101}
102static inline fdt32_t cpu_to_fdt32(uint32_t x)
103{
104 return (FDT_FORCE fdt32_t)CPU_TO_FDT32(x);
105}
106
107static inline uint64_t fdt64_to_cpu(fdt64_t x)
108{
109 return (FDT_FORCE uint64_t)CPU_TO_FDT64(x);
110}
111static inline fdt64_t cpu_to_fdt64(uint64_t x)
112{
113 return (FDT_FORCE fdt64_t)CPU_TO_FDT64(x);
114}
115#undef CPU_TO_FDT64
116#undef CPU_TO_FDT32
117#undef CPU_TO_FDT16
118#undef EXTRACT_BYTE
119
120#endif /* _LIBFDT_ENV_H */
